Description: Provides Bayesian inference methods for infectious disease
        transmission models in healthcare settings. Implements Markov
        Chain Monte Carlo (MCMC) algorithms for estimating transmission
        parameters from patient-level data including admission,
        discharge, and testing events as described in Thomas 'et al.'
        (2015) <doi:10.1093/imammb/dqt021>.
